#### 2. Workspace 配置

```yaml
# pnpm-workspace.yaml
packages:
  - 'packages/*'
  - 'examples/*'
```

#### 3. SDK package.json

```json
{
  "name": "@liuma/auth-sdk",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "type": "module",
